parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Strut Tower Corrosion and Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and failure of the front strut tower can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: corrosion and rust on the front strut tower
and fracture of the strut tower.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Warped Brake Rotors and Pulsating Brake Pedal
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Warped brake rotors can cause the brake pedal to pulsate, leading to uneven braking performance, which can increase the stopping distance and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: Pulsating feel in the brake pedal
pushback by the pedal during hard stops
pulsating feel in the steering wheel
and vibration in the vehicle during normal driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and stability, leading to accidents or loss of control.
The failure to replace recalled parts can lead to safety risks, accidents, and injuries, as the defective parts can cause the vehicle to malfunction or fail.
symptoms: as the issue is related to the failure to repair or replace recalled parts.
